{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1014,"text":"I'll begin today"},{"time":2825,"text":"by sharing a poem"},{"time":4891,"text":"written by my friend from Malawi,"},{"time":8026,"text":"Eileen Piri."},{"time":10162,"text":"Eileen is only 13 years old,"},{"time":13506,"text":"but when we were going through\nthe collection of poetry that we wrote,"},{"time":19380,"text":"I found her poem so interesting,"},{"time":22248,"text":"so motivating."},{"time":24245,"text":"So I'll read it to you."},{"time":26905,"text":"She entitled her poem\n\"I'll Marry When I Want.\""},{"time":30503,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":33359,"text":"\"I'll marry when I want."},{"time":35890,"text":"My mother can't force me to marry."},{"time":40790,"text":"My father cannot force me to marry."},{"time":45526,"text":"My uncle, my aunt,"},{"time":48336,"text":"my brother or sister,"},{"time":50681,"text":"cannot force me to marry."},{"time":53885,"text":"No one in the world"},{"time":56254,"text":"can force me to marry."},{"time":59550,"text":"I'll marry when I want."},{"time":62499,"text":"Even if you beat me,"},{"time":65077,"text":"even if you chase me away,"},{"time":67747,"text":"even if you do anything bad to me,"},{"time":70928,"text":"I'll marry when I want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74364,"text":"I'll marry when I want,"},{"time":77267,"text":"but not before I am well educated,"},{"time":81005,"text":"and not before I am all grown up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85323,"text":"I'll marry when I want.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":88831,"text":"This poem might seem odd,"},{"time":91827,"text":"written by a 13-year-old girl,"},{"time":95356,"text":"but where I and Eileen come from,"},{"time":100139,"text":"this poem, which I have just read to you,"},{"time":103900,"text":"is a warrior's cry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107616,"text":"I am from Malawi."},{"time":111191,"text":"Malawi is one of the poorest countries,"},{"time":115115,"text":"very poor,"},{"time":117994,"text":"where gender equality is questionable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122522,"text":"Growing up in that country,"},{"time":124844,"text":"I couldn't make my own choices in life."},{"time":128095,"text":"I couldn't even explore"},{"time":130393,"text":"personal opportunities in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133389,"text":"I will tell you a story"},{"time":135919,"text":"of two different girls,"},{"time":138381,"text":"two beautiful girls."},{"time":142026,"text":"These girls grew up"},{"time":144580,"text":"under the same roof."},{"time":146693,"text":"They were eating the same food."},{"time":149410,"text":"Sometimes, they would share clothes,"},{"time":152173,"text":"and even shoes."},{"time":154982,"text":"But their lives ended up differently,"},{"time":159649,"text":"in two different paths."},{"time":163039,"text":"The other girl is my little sister."},{"time":166754,"text":"My little sister was only 11 years old"},{"time":171677,"text":"when she got pregnant."},{"time":176029,"text":"It's a hurtful thing."},{"time":181352,"text":"Not only did it hurt her, even me."},{"time":184633,"text":"I was going through a hard time as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188232,"text":"As it is in my culture,"},{"time":191947,"text":"once you reach puberty stage,"},{"time":194942,"text":"you are supposed to go\nto initiation camps."},{"time":198820,"text":"In these initiation camps,"},{"time":201118,"text":"you are taught how\nto sexually please a man."},{"time":204973,"text":"There is this special day,"},{"time":206761,"text":"which they call \"Very Special Day\""},{"time":209965,"text":"where a man who is hired\nby the community"},{"time":212519,"text":"comes to the camp"},{"time":215143,"text":"and sleeps with the little girls."},{"time":219252,"text":"Imagine the trauma that these young girls\n"},{"time":221766,"text":"go through every day."},{"time":226766,"text":"Most girls end up pregnant."},{"time":229925,"text":"They even contract HIV and AIDS\n"},{"time":232542,"text":"and other sexually transmitted diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235692,"text":"For my little sister,\nshe ended up being pregnant."},{"time":240603,"text":"Today, she's only 16 years old"},{"time":244666,"text":"and she has three children."},{"time":247662,"text":"Her first marriage did not survive,"},{"time":251307,"text":"nor did her second marriage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254604,"text":"On the other side, there is this girl."},{"time":259341,"text":"She's amazing."},{"time":261314,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":263218,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":267723,"text":"I call her amazing because she is."},{"time":270138,"text":"She's very fabulous."},{"time":273203,"text":"That girl is me. (Laughter)"},{"time":276964,"text":"When I was 13 years old,"},{"time":279982,"text":"I was told, you are grown up,"},{"time":283396,"text":"you have now reached of age,"},{"time":286228,"text":"you're supposed to go\nto the initiation camp."},{"time":289595,"text":"I was like, \"What?"},{"time":292567,"text":"I'm not going to go\nto the initiation camps.\""},{"time":298349,"text":"You know what the women said to me?"},{"time":301112,"text":"\"You are a stupid girl. Stubborn."},{"time":304734,"text":"You do not respect the traditions\nof our society, of our community.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":312001,"text":"I said no because I knew\nwhere I was going."},{"time":315809,"text":"I knew what I wanted in life."},{"time":319773,"text":"I had a lot of dreams as a young girl."},{"time":324238,"text":"I wanted to get well educated,"},{"time":327883,"text":"to find a decent job in the future."},{"time":330363,"text":"I was imagining myself as a lawyer,\n"},{"time":332122,"text":"seated on that big chair."},{"time":334832,"text":"Those were the imaginations that\n"},{"time":337138,"text":"were going through my mind every day."},{"time":340468,"text":"And I knew that one day,"},{"time":342302,"text":"I would contribute something,\na little something to my community."},{"time":346876,"text":"But every day after refusing,"},{"time":349407,"text":"women would tell me,"},{"time":351427,"text":"\"Look at you, you're all grown up.\nYour little sister has a baby."},{"time":354817,"text":"What about you?\""},{"time":356303,"text":"That was the music\nthat I was hearing every day,"},{"time":361017,"text":"and that is the music\nthat girls hear every day"},{"time":364894,"text":"when they don't do something\nthat the community needs them to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371524,"text":"When I compared the two stories\nbetween me and my sister,"},{"time":375448,"text":"I said, \"Why can't I do something?"},{"time":380185,"text":"Why can't I change something\nthat has happened for a long time"},{"time":385246,"text":"in our community?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":387661,"text":"That was when I called other girls"},{"time":390169,"text":"just like my sister, who have children,"},{"time":392723,"text":"who have been in class but they have\nforgotten how to read and write."},{"time":396187,"text":"I said, \"Come on, we can \nremind each other"},{"time":398297,"text":"how to read and write again,"},{"time":400432,"text":"how to hold the pen,\nhow to read, to hold the book.\""},{"time":404240,"text":"It was a great time I had with them."},{"time":407885,"text":"Nor did I just learn a little about them,"},{"time":412157,"text":"but they were able to tell me\ntheir personal stories,"},{"time":415594,"text":"what they were facing every day"},{"time":417405,"text":"as young mothers."},{"time":420075,"text":"That was when I was like,"},{"time":422072,"text":"'Why can't we take all these things\nthat are happening to us"},{"time":425996,"text":"and present them and tell our mothers,\nour traditional leaders,"},{"time":429873,"text":"that these are the wrong things?\""},{"time":431870,"text":"It was a scary thing to do,"},{"time":433937,"text":"because these traditional leaders,"},{"time":435910,"text":"they are already accustomed to the things\n"},{"time":438114,"text":"that have been there for ages."},{"time":440554,"text":"A hard thing to change,"},{"time":442481,"text":"but a good thing to try."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445105,"text":"So we tried."},{"time":447357,"text":"It was very hard, but we pushed."},{"time":450245,"text":"And I'm here to say that in my community,\n"},{"time":453109,"text":"it was the first community after girls\n"},{"time":455669,"text":"pushed so hard to our traditional leader,\n"},{"time":459036,"text":"and our leader stood up for us\nand said no girl has to be married"},{"time":463425,"text":"before the age of 18."},{"time":465654,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":473502,"text":"In my community,"},{"time":475243,"text":"that was the first time a community,"},{"time":477890,"text":"they had to call the bylaws,"},{"time":480351,"text":"the first bylaw that protected girls"},{"time":483858,"text":"in our community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486052,"text":"We did not stop there."},{"time":487840,"text":"We forged ahead."},{"time":490789,"text":"We were determined to fight for girls\nnot just in my community,"},{"time":494643,"text":"but even in other communities."},{"time":497429,"text":"When the child marriage bill\nwas being presented in February,"},{"time":501562,"text":"we were there at the Parliament house."},{"time":505208,"text":"Every day, when the members\nof Parliament were entering,"},{"time":509294,"text":"we were telling them,\n\"Would you please support the bill?\""},{"time":512383,"text":"And we don't have\nmuch technology like here,"},{"time":517142,"text":"but we have our small phones."},{"time":519139,"text":"So we said, \"Why can't we get \ntheir numbers and text them?\""},{"time":524178,"text":"So we did that. It was a good thing."},{"time":527428,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":529448,"text":"So when the bill passed,\nwe texted them back,"},{"time":532421,"text":"\"Thank you for supporting the bill.\""},{"time":534849,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":535919,"text":"And when the bill was signed\nby the president,"},{"time":539264,"text":"making it into law, it was a plus."},{"time":542630,"text":"Now, in Malawi, 18 is the legal\nmarriage age, from 15 to 18."},{"time":548482,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":554495,"text":"It's a good thing to know\nthat the bill passed,"},{"time":558071,"text":"but let me tell you this:"},{"time":561113,"text":"There are countries where 18\nis the legal marriage age,"},{"time":565501,"text":"but don't we hear cries\nof women and girls every day?"},{"time":569773,"text":"Every day, girls' lives\nare being wasted away."},{"time":575416,"text":"This is high time for leaders\nto honor their commitment."},{"time":581870,"text":"In honoring this commitment,"},{"time":584239,"text":"it means keeping girls' issues\nat heart every time."},{"time":589951,"text":"We don't have to be subjected as second,"},{"time":593712,"text":"but they have to know that women,\nas we are in this room,"},{"time":597950,"text":"we are not just women,\nwe are not just girls,"},{"time":601000,"text":"we are extraordinary."},{"time":602980,"text":"We can do more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604893,"text":"And another thing for Malawi,"},{"time":607888,"text":"and not just Malawi but other countries:"},{"time":610790,"text":"The laws which are there,"},{"time":614575,"text":"you know how a law is not a law\nuntil it is enforced?"},{"time":620426,"text":"The law which has just recently passed"},{"time":623839,"text":"and the laws that in other countries\nhave been there,"},{"time":626463,"text":"they need to be publicized\nat the local level,"},{"time":630387,"text":"at the community level,"},{"time":632570,"text":"where girls' issues are very striking."},{"time":637956,"text":"Girls face issues, difficult issues,\nat the community level every day."},{"time":643274,"text":"So if these young girls know\nthat there are laws that protect them,"},{"time":648359,"text":"they will be able to stand up\nand defend themselves"},{"time":651145,"text":"because they will know that\nthere is a law that protects them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657254,"text":"And another thing I would say is that"},{"time":661363,"text":"girls' voices and women's voices"},{"time":665961,"text":"are beautiful, they are there,"},{"time":668724,"text":"but we cannot do this alone."},{"time":671905,"text":"Male advocates, they have to jump in,"},{"time":674575,"text":"to step in and work together."},{"time":676525,"text":"It's a collective work."},{"time":679103,"text":"What we need is what girls elsewhere need:"},{"time":681843,"text":"good education, and above all,\nnot to marry whilst 11."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690085,"text":"And furthermore,"},{"time":692953,"text":"I know that together,"},{"time":696018,"text":"we can transform the legal,"},{"time":699966,"text":"the cultural and political framework"},{"time":703135,"text":"that denies girls of their rights."},{"time":707906,"text":"I am standing here today"},{"time":712964,"text":"and declaring that we can\nend child marriage in a generation."},{"time":720677,"text":"This is the moment"},{"time":722860,"text":"where a girl and a girl,\nand millions of girls worldwide,"},{"time":727294,"text":"will be able to say,"},{"time":729895,"text":"\"I will marry when I want.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":733099,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":743284,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}